result.title: Warm-up Contest
result.content:
To all members of Next Lab Programming Varsity, we will be having a warm-up contest on Tuesday, from 4:30 PM to 6:30 PM.

Please click on the "Contests" tab to view it. Alternatively, you can register using this link.

It will be used to test your current abilities. Problems are varied, and only has a difficulty of a regular Div. 2 round. I am sure you will have fun with them. Good luck!
